column5: Does anyone know if Kitfisher changed his name here?  Or know how I can contact him?  Thanks, Pam.

Pamela,  I think he changed his name to FishNAutographs.  I also had his site bookmarked, you may be able to contact him thru there  http://www.dssports.ca/Contact.htm  He is off at Police College now I think so not been on in awhile  Hope this helps.
